doc_68fb36b2a83536.91204382.text: DataPizza-AI-PHP is a framework for building AI applications in pure PHP. It supports RAG, embeddings, ReAct agents and various tools.

doc_68fb36b5c767a6.61220740.text: The framework includes 6 LLM providers: OpenAI, DeepSeek, Claude, Gemini, Mistral and Kimi. All OpenAI API compatible.

doc_68fb36b8adbbe1.69710951.text: Available tools: Calculator for math, DateTime for dates, Wikipedia for searches, FileReader for files, DuckDuckGo for web search.

doc_68fb36bba7c218.30525690.text: Modular architecture with ingestion pipeline, prompt templates, conversation memory, vector search and n8n/MCP integration.
